\ls1\ilvl0
\b0\fs48 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1 carton Cold Stone Creamery ice cream (recommended: "Everybody's" flavor, with or without mix-ins)\
{\listtext	\'95	}Cake bottom of your choice*\
{\listtext	\'95	}Prepared frozen whipped topping, thawed or prepared whipped cream or softened buttercream (recommended: Cool Whip or Reddi-Wip)\
